Text:
OBS: This file only works if you havent installed the Demo version before!

eg: you need a system reg without any Fraps keys... 

Basic and safe way to clean your registry is to reinstall windows :)

ENJOY!

If FRAPS won't start it's because you downloaded the demo version and certain registry entries need to be cleaned out.  Just follow the instructions on this link:

http://www.raymond.cc/blog/archives/2007/09/14/fix-fraps-not-opening-problem/

and it will fix the problem.
